msg.vmplayer.nativeVmrcHelpText = "使用方法: vmrc.exe <URL>|0A其中 <URL> 语法如下: vmrc://[<user>|7C(<ticket-type>:<ticket>)@]<host>[:<port>]/|0A ?moid=<VM-id>[&httpproxy=<proxy server>[:<proxy port>]|0A [&proxyuser=<proxy username>][&proxypasswd=<proxy auth password>]]0A或使用以下语法: vmrc://settings|0A|0A 示例: vmrc://clone:ticket@vsphere-server/?moid=42|0A 示例: vmrc://username@vsphere-server/?moid=79|0A 示例: vmrc://<host>[:port]/?moid=1&httpproxy=<server>&proxyuser=<name>|0A 示例: vmrc://settings|0A|0A提示:|0A <proxy username> 或 <proxy auth password>|0A 中的字符「&」必须编码为「%26」。|0A|0A以下参数可用于 MKS 连接:|0A &websocket=<WebSocket URL>|0A &mksticket=<ticket>|0A &thumbprint=<SSL thumbprint>|0A &path=<VM path>|0A|0A 示例: vmrc://vRAserver/?thumbprint=aa:bb:cc|0A &websocket=wss://host:443/ticket/123|0A"
